entry.content:
Background

This reading group was started by Sanchayan Dutta, a math student at UC Davis who is also interested in computational complexity and some members of the Kim Lab. Since this is an ongoing activity I plan on updating it as we go. So far the plan is to follow along roughly with Dr. Henry Yuen's complexity notes:

Advanced Topics in Quantum Information Theory
